â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• *@
@if (onglet == "achats")
{
    <div class="toolbar" style="margin-top:12px">
        <div class="toolbar-filters" style="flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px">
            @foreach (var tf in TypesAchat)
            {
                <button class="btn-secondary @(filtreTypeAchat==tf.Id?"btn-active":"")"
                        @onclick="() => SetFiltreAchat(tf.Id)">@tf.Libelle</button>
            }
        </div>
        <div class="search-box">
            <span class="search-icon">🔍</span>
            <input class="search-input" type="text" placeholder="N°, fournisseur..."
                   @bind="rechercheAchat" @bind:event="oninput" />
        </div>
    </div>

    @if (chargementAchats) { <div class="loading-state"><div class="spinner-lg"></div></div> }
    else
    {
        <div class="table-container">
            <table class="data-table">
                <thead><tr>
                    <th>N° Document</th><th>Type</th><th>Fournisseur</th><th>Date</th>
                    <th>Livraison prévue</th><th class="text-right">TTC</th>
                    <th class="text-right">Solde</th><th>Statut</th><th>Actions</th>
                </tr></thead>
                <tbody>
                @foreach (var d in AchatsFiltres)
                {
                    <tr class="@(d.EstVerrouille?"row-locked":"")">
                        <td><code class="mono">@d.Numero</code></td>
                        <td><span class="badge @GetBadgeAchat(d.TypeDocument)">@d.TypeLibelle</span></td>
                        <td class="cell-main">@d.FournisseurNom</td>
                        <td class="small text-muted">@d.DateDocument.ToString("dd/MM/yyyy")</td>
                        <td class="small text-muted">@(d.DateLivraisonPrevue?.ToString("dd/MM/yyyy") ?? "—")</td>
                        <td class="text-right mono">@d.MontantTTC.ToString("N2") F</td>
                        <td class="text-right mono @(d.Solde>0&&d.TypeDocument==4?"text-warn":"")">@d.Solde.ToString("N2") F</td>
                        <td><span class="badge @GetStatutBadgeAchat(d.Statut)">@d.StatutLibelle</span>
                            @if (d.EstVerrouille) { <span title="Réglé">Verrouillé</span> }</td>
                        <td class="actions-cell">
                            @if (d.TypeDocument < 4 && !d.EstVerrouille)
                            {
                                <details class="row-actions-menu">
                                    <summary class="btn-row-action btn-row-action--soft" type="button">Actions</summary>
                                    <div class="row-actions-menu-list">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-row-action btn-row-action--primary" @onclick="() => OuvrirConsultationAchat(d)">Consulter</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-row-action btn-row-action--print" @onclick="() => ImprimerAchat(d)">Imprimer</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-row-action btn-row-action--warn" @onclick="() => OuvrirTransfoAchat(d)">Transformer</button>
                                    </div>
                                </details>
                            }
                            else
                            {
                                <details class="row-actions-menu">
                                    <summary class="btn-row-action btn-row-action--soft" type="button">Actions</summary>
                                    <div class="row-actions-menu-list">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-row-action btn-row-action--primary" @onclick="() => OuvrirConsultationAchat(d)">Consulter</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-row-action btn-row-action--print" @onclick="() => ImprimerAchat(d)">Imprimer</button>
                                    </div>
                                </details>
                            }
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                }
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        @if (!achats.Any()) { <div class="empty-state">Aucun document d'achat. Cliquez "+ Nouveau document".</div> }
    }
}

